<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī Amōghavariṣaṁ pṛthuvīrājyaṁge[yye Ā]
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tana priyatanayātmajanindambanavāsi pa<unclear>nnicchā</unclear>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>siramumanāḷuttire Ātana manōnayanavallabhe gōyi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ndabbe [Ū]ranāḷe kaliyammannāḻgāmuṇḍu geye tivu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḻarā mārammagōsāsi niṟi
<lb n="6" break="no"/>sidō mēṇṭiya
</p>

